  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the girl uncovers the truth of her past, she gradually overcomes her trauma. <br>Join the wounded girl on her journey to find her true self. <br>Disorder is a roguelike dungeon crawler.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332340/extras/0b8bbde6aae5a1d4e4815730d4a8c334.poster.avif?t=1751944338\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332340/extras/0b8bbde6aae5a1d4e4815730d4a8c334.webm?t=1751944338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332340/extras/0b8bbde6aae5a1d4e4815730d4a8c334.mp4?t=1751944338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Fight to Reclaim Your Memories</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a girl who has lost her memories and uncover the truth. The story unfolds as you grow stronger with each escape attempt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332340/extras/497b8dfec8c49cf7e9fcd5706eb39669.poster.avif?t=1751944338\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332340/extras/497b8dfec8c49cf7e9fcd5706eb39669.webm?t=1751944338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332340/extras/497b8dfec8c49cf7e9fcd5706eb39669.mp4?t=1751944338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Designed for Replayability</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The department store is constantly changing, offering a new experience with every run. <br>Use the Gift Desk to become stronger and acquire abilities to tackle your next escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332340/extras/ff0835e6b9ec9bc61f4581ac1a52b784.poster.avif?t=1751944338\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332340/extras/ff0835e6b9ec9bc61f4581ac1a52b784.webm?t=1751944338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1332340/extras/ff0835e6b9ec9bc61f4581ac1a52b784.mp4?t=1751944338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No Failure in Any Challenge</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even if you're not an expert player, anyone can enjoy the flashy skills and exciting story through permanent enhancements. <br>Are you a pro? It’s time to put your controls to the test. Take the challenge!</p>",
